{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"custom_css":[".sidebar-content {font-family: MCM-BOLD-EXTEND !important;}",".main-content {font-family: MCM-BOLD-EXTEND !important;}"],"settings":{}},"custom_liquid_BGa88C":{"type":"custom-liquid","custom_css":["{margin: 0 5%;}"],"settings":{"custom_liquid":"<style><!--\n  .mcm-mirum-products {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    color: #000;\n    width: 100%;\ndisplay: flex;\n  }\n\n  .mcm-mirum-products h1 {\n    font-size: 24px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .mcm-mirum-products p {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n\n  .mcm-mirum-products img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n  }\n.mcm-mirum-products.text {\n    display: flex\n;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    margin-right: 5% !important;\n    text-align: left;\n    justify-content: center;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n}\n--><\/style>\n<div class=\"mcm-mirum-products\">\n<div class=\"mcm-mirum-products text\">\n<h1>MIRUM®<\/h1>\n<p>Traditional leather alternatives are heavily reliant on fossil-fuel derived synthetics, which do not biodegrade and contribute to the global plastic issue. That’s why we are proud to partner with NFW to introduce MIRUM® alternative leather into the design and manufacture of our products. As a naturally circular, scalable, 100% plastic and water-free material, MIRUM® an incredibly exciting resource for us.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mcm-mirum-products img\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.media.amplience.net\/i\/mcmworldwide\/MIRUM_MCMEdit_IMG1?$poi$&amp;w=1920&amp;fmt=auto&amp;qlt=default&amp;sm=aspect&amp;aspect=4:5\" alt=\"MIRUM Product Image\"><\/div>\n<\/div>"}},"video_block_RkHVew":{"type":"video-block","settings":{"container":"container","spotlight_bg":"#ffffff","spotlight_bg_gradient":"","video_block_title":"","color_title":"#232323","fontsize_title":16,"fontsize_title_mb":22,"margin_bottom_title":45,"video_block_des":"","color_des":"#3c3c3c","fontsize_des":16,"tit